  "body": "For weird reasons, IsAuthenticated is not working in these two places as expected:\r\n\r\n1. https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/master/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.JsonRpc/JsonRpcProcessor.cs#L178\r\n2. https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/master/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Runner/JsonRpc/Startup.cs#L201\r\n\r\nThe expectation is MaxBatchSize and MaxBatchResponseBodySize should be ignored for requests from CL (on the authenticated port).\r\nTo debug this issue we can set MaxBatchSize and later MaxBatchResponseBodySize to low value and run Nethermind with CL.\r\n\r\nLet's debug it and fix it.",
